title: Spearow
description: Inept at flying high. However, it can fly around very fast to protect its territory.

title: Alcremie
description: Cream Pokemon. Evolved from a milcery holds a sweet and is spun by the player; Edited by Matthew

title: Ash Greninja
description: When it retracts its long neck into its shell, it squirts out water with vigorous force.

title: Jigglypuff
description: When its huge eyes waver, it sings a mysteriously soothing melody that lulls its enemies to sleep.

title: Venusaur
description: By spreading the broad petals of its flower and catching the sun's rays, it fills its body with power

title: Litten
description: It spews fire from its nostrils. While it is an adorable Fire Cat Pokémon, its temper is not to be taken lightly.

title: Umbreon
description: This Dark Pokémon evolved from Eevee exposed to the moon’s rays. It hides silently in darkness and waits for its foes.

title: Lucario
description: A Pokémon that can sense auras to track and hunt down opponents. It understands human speech and is loyal to its master.

title: Pikachu
description: This Electric-type Pokémon is capable of releasing electric discharges of varying intensity.

title: Eevee
description: Known for its unstable genetic makeup, this normal-type Pokémon can evolve into a variety of forms depending on its environment.

title: Garchomp
description: Garchomp, the Mach Pokémon, flies at speeds equal to a jet fighter plane. It never allows its prey to escape.
